A simple notifier for when chat messages come in via Gmail's built-in
chat, built on top of Mozilla Labs Jetpack: 

    https://jetpack.mozillalabs.com/

Source lives in Github:

    http://github.com/joeshaw/gchat-jetpack-notifier

And the "live" code is here for now:

    http://joeshaw.org/jetpacks/gchat-jetpack-notifier/gchat-notifier.html
